	FACT:Worshippers|Anuirean,Barbarian,Fighter,Paladin
	FACTSET:Pantheon|Birthright
	FACTSET:Race|Human
	DESC:Cuiraécen (Anuire), Kirche (Brechtür), Khirdai (Khinasi), Kirken (Rjurik). Cuiraécen (koo-RAY-eh-KEN) is the son of Haelyn and Nesirie. The god of battle is the patron of young warriors, for he is the representation of reckless courage and victory through strength.
	SYMBOL:Lightning bolt crossed by a sword
	DOMAINS:Chaos,Good,Strength,Storm,War|PREALIGN:NG,CG,N,CN,NE,CE

