Eloéle
	KEY:Eloéle
	SORTKEY:01_Birthright
	ALIGN:CN
	FACT:Title|Sister of Thieves
	FACT:Symbol|Black dagger
	FACT:Worshippers|Rogue
	FACTSET:Pantheon|Birthright
	FACTSET:Race|Human
	DESC:Eloéle (Anuire), Éla (Brechtür), Elyal (Vosgaard). Eloéle (eh-LOW-eh-lay) is the lady of the night and the mistress of thieves, spies, and others who hide their activities from view. She deceives as naturally as others breathe; those who lie by design or habit also take her as their patron.
	SYMBOL:Black dagger
	DOMAINS:Chaos,Illusion,Night,Trickery|PREALIGN:NG,CG,N,CN,NE,CE

